\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Elrahet nodded. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It was his final meal.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93This place is cursed,\u8221\'94 said Moto.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Cursed!?\u8221\'94 exclaimed Elrahet. \u8220\'93Nonsense. This man was one of Solraheen\u8217\'92s champions.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93How could you say that?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t be so quick to judge those touched by the darkness. There is no greater struggle. And this brave soul was victorious. He fought against the rising tide and cut out his own stomach before it took him completely. See here\u8230\'85 he was growing horns.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 She turned the man\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s chin upright with the tip of her cane, and sure enough, there were two fleshy nubs protruding from his forehead. His jaw lolled open, and a long, forked tongue unfurled onto the floor.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If he had lost his battle, this world\u8217\'92s woes would be magnified by a hundred thousand thousand.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 She held the torch low to the slumped form of the green-robed man. On the ground in front of him, half buried in ash, was a round stomach that was so inflated with that final meal that it seemed close to bursting. It was still attached to man\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s intestines, and  and that it resembled a  was as nearly. Not to mention that it was nearly as black as fabled black.}
