\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Feel no sympathy,\u8221\'94 said Elrahet, \u8220\'93for his fate may be our own. Demons come for our very Sparks and so you must kill yourselves lest they capture you alive.\u8221\'94}
